owltools.mooncat

Class PropertyExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • owltools.mooncat.PropertyExtractor

  • public class PropertyExtractor
extends Object
    Author:
    cjm Extracts a set of properties from an ontology O The extracted properties will also include follow the reference closure of those properties, along axioms such as InverseOf, SubPropertyOf. Annotation assertion axioms are also collected
